headline.print_headline: Walt Disney, Shanghai Media Group to Develop Disney-Branded Movies
headline.main: Walt Disney, Shanghai Media Group to Develop Disney-Branded Movies

lead_paragraph: Walt Disney Studios has signed an agreement with Shanghai Media Group Pictures to develop Disney-branded movies, the latest move by a U.S. studio to grow its presence in China's entertainment business.
